ts, the Amazon Payments account used to receive funds raised on Kickstart=
er must be set up as a 501(c)(3) organization. For more information about=
 how to set up an Amazon Payments account as a non-profit please reach ou=
t to [Amazon Payments directly](https://payments.amazon.com/sdui/sdui/con=
tactussend).

As for tax deductible funding, in general, funds raised on Kickstarter ar=
e subject to taxes. How much you owe can vary based on a number of factor=
s, including the deduction of project-related expenses. We highly recomme=
nd talking to an accountant or tax advisor. They can guide you through yo=
ur particular tax scenario in the most advantageous way possible. There's=
 a bit more information about this in our [Tax Guide](https://www.kicksta=
rter.com/help/taxes).

